ygData.messageBody:
When I went for the Opoline helm I was grouped with my friends. I am level
30, They were level 50 bard and level 50 magician w/ pet. Once we got the
deepwater gobs on land they were rather easy but they beat the hell out of
the 50 bard in the cavern. Most of it is going to require groups of low to
mid 30's to get. The basalt carapace and Gypsy lute may require a bigger
group, of course.

Good Journey,

Sineras Silverlyre (Cazic-Thule)
